reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 6, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars The look is pretty nice for $54!
reviews.reviewText: Easy to put together BUT we had two bags of screws that said # 2. One one obviously a 3, so be mindful that the long %2's are actually the 3's if your package comes like that.Drawers are fabric fold ones, but we won't be using them, so not a deal breaker for us.Would def buy again!

reviews.reviewerName: Very effective and affordable Very effective and affordable
reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 7, 2024
reviews.reviewText: This bedside stand has a great quality and suits the purpose for which it was bought for. Both arrived on time and it was very easy to assemble. I strongly recommend.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 14, 2023
reviews.reviewText: It's smaller than your average so it's great for smaller homes and rooms 👌 I was hoping the whole drawer would be wood but it's partial wood and cloth. Part of it came chipped and some of the metal came bent. Was able to smack it out but not the BEST QUALITY - but sturdyThe instructions were clear and easy to read. Took me like an hour, hour and a half to put them both together.The back panel is great, I'm gonna use mounting tape to attach a extention :)

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 27, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great but short
reviews.reviewText: It’s a really sturdy easy to build night table, and it is really cute! They are a bit small though so be warned :)

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 21, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Nice for the money, but...
reviews.reviewText: These are super simple to put together. I actually like the fabric "faux wood" looking drawer. Only issue I have is one of the tops had a big scratch or it would have been 5 stars

reviews.reviewText: I love these pair of nightstands. They were super simple to put together took me about 20 minutes to put them both together. They really add a nice touch and I like the fact the height is adjustable.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 27, 2024

reviews.reviewText: These are easy to put togeather and great for small spaces ! I will note that the drawr is fabric so if you do not like that its not for you

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 27, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Great value, light weight but not too sturdy
reviews.reviewText: Purchased these for my basement/den area. Required assembly. Not hard to build. Not heavy.The actual drawer unit itself is a bit flimsy. Won't hold a lot of weight. But its OK for light duty use.
